## Troubleshooting

### Common Issues

{% if language == 'python' %}
**Command not found after pipx install:**
```bash
pipx ensurepath
source ~/.bashrc  # or restart terminal
```

**Permission errors:**
```bash
# Use pipx instead of pip for global installations
pipx install {{ installation.pypi_name | default(package_name) }}
```
{% elif language in ['nodejs', 'typescript'] %}
**Command not found after npm install:**
```bash
# Check npm global bin directory
npm config get prefix
# Add to PATH if necessary
export PATH=$PATH:$(npm config get prefix)/bin
```

**Permission errors on global install:**
```bash
# Use npx for one-time execution
npx {{ installation.npm_name | default(package_name) }}

# Or fix npm permissions
npm config set prefix ~/.npm-global
export PATH=$PATH:~/.npm-global/bin
```
{% elif language == 'rust' %}
**Command not found after cargo install:**
```bash
# Ensure cargo bin directory is in PATH
source ~/.cargo/env
# or manually add to PATH
export PATH=$PATH:~/.cargo/bin
```

**Build failures:**
```bash
# Update Rust toolchain
rustup update stable

# Clear cargo cache
cargo clean
```
{% endif %}

